Ranger Help for: rcommand
=========================

SYNTAX:      rcommand <follower> <action>
USAGE:       Any terrain

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to issue a command to their bonded animal
follower. The follower will attempt to carry out the action to the
best of its ability. Common commands include attacking a target,
staying in place, following the Ranger, or performing trained tricks.
The follower must be in the same room as the Ranger to receive
commands. Not all animals can perform all actions - the available
commands depend on the follower's species and training.
